import * as S from './Intro.styled'
import * as T from '../../../components/Typography'
import * as G from '../../../components/Grid'
import ImageFull from '../../../components/ImageFull'

const Intro = () => (
    <S.IntroWrapper>
        <S.ContentWrapper>
                <T.SubHeading>Product design</T.SubHeading>
                <G.XSmall/>
                <T.Display>Envelopes payments</T.Display>
        </S.ContentWrapper>
        <ImageFull/>
    </S.IntroWrapper>
    

)

export default Intro
